Title: Brane Dynamics and Gauge Theory

Authors: A. Giveon, D. Kutasov

Comments: 291 pages, 52 figures; expanded introduction and minor changes

Journal-ref: Rev.Mod.Phys. 71 (1999) 983-1084

We review some aspects of the interplay between the dynamics of branes instring theory and the classical and quantum physics of gauge theories withdifferent numbers of supersymmetries in various dimensions.